{"tid":580731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：支持財政司司長不宜派錢看法","createTime":"2018-03-04T17:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T17:54:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"769b4ede06b59bd4de636fa9d5f25e5bcd84b76d","tid":580731,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T17:40:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1383791-20180304.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1383791-20180304.htm&d=pEmv80Ww3uRh8MVoZrTHPy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=d6d5e33d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1383791-20180304.htm&h=fafa5c1f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1383791-20180304.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥，出發往北京列席兩會前見記者。她被問到政府是否堅持不會全民派錢時說，派錢一般並無針對性，即每人可領取相同金額，財政司司長原則性認為不適宜，她亦支持有關看法。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，派錢做法並非受到全社會認同，社評與政黨亦非一致贊成以派錢方式分享經濟成果，重申政府希望公共資源用於較有需要人士身上。"},{"pid":"0379cc8b81f5261090824fe8fe49cf2d391b0236","tid":580731,"uid":143915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T17:43:13.000Z","msg":"New fiscal philosophy <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc11ba91528983f1d2030ca2c104d36efedcfdfa","tid":580731,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T17:43:15.000Z","msg":"大業主有冇需要 你答我呀八婆！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大聲啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未食飯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45250676658f6982c2dbefc7f43a5d867a13848b","tid":580731,"uid":27688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T17:43:34.000Z","msg":"貼去港人港地睇下班藍絲咩反應..."},{"pid":"4f672748a84fbd8b2f3f1e6c97007c10bc4